Text: Rikki65 I take a look around will gave you in mind :)

The video is decent, but I have seen (and converted on my own) 720p video that looked much better than this transfer. The audio, unfortunately, renders this unwatchable. The volume is very low, and the channels are all off-kilter (dialogue, which should be in the center, was delegated to the right front speaker). A very poor job, I must say.
